{"tid":751384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"珀麗灣業主立案法團倡補貼離島渡輪服務","createTime":"2018-07-21T22:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T10:43:27.000Z","uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b508f645da2b09a2721d617f6e91204e46745ba3","tid":751384,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T22:18:21.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】運輸署否決珀麗灣客運有限公司縮減中環來往馬灣航線班次申請。<br />\n<br />\n約一千名居民早前集會，抗議屋苑的客運公司申請削減航線每天六班非繁忙時段的渡輪班次，運輸署與業主委員會及客運公司會面，並公布否決申請。<br />\n<br />\n署方重申根據協議，發展商有責任提供妥善的渡輪服務和巴士服務往來馬灣，運輸署在審批交通服務的調整時，會以居民的需要為首要考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">業主立案法團歡迎署方決定，但認為政府長遠應補貼離島的渡輪服務，令客運公司有經濟誘因繼續經營航線。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%8F%80%E9%BA%97%E7%81%A3%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E7%AB%8B%E6%A1%88%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%98%E5%80%A1%E8%A3%9C%E8%B2%BC%E9%9B%A2%E5%B3%B6%E6%B8%A1%E8%BC%AA%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99-155326019.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%258F%2580%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%2598%25E5%2580%25A1%25E8%25A3%259C%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599-155326019.html&d=KVXReHL18IQ%2FliS%2BhPGK%2FghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7a6da4ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%8F%80%E9%BA%97%E7%81%A3%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E7%AB%8B%E6%A1%88%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%98%E5%80%A1%E8%A3%9C%E8%B2%BC%E9%9B%A2%E5%B3%B6%E6%B8%A1%E8%BC%AA%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99-155326019.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319fff0774aae843ba2087c389ef8ae2b38a70c2","tid":751384,"uid":18948,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T22:44:45.000Z","msg":"補貼？<br />\n<br />\n啱呀，加你地自己啲管理費補囉"},{"pid":"e841e5e52ee32d53d00ef7bdd17d5c9ee50ee